name: Roy G. Blob
description:
Interactive RGB color blob

Keyboard Controls
[Space] Toggle Dark Mode
[W] Increment speed
[S] Decrement speed
[D] Increment sides
[A] Decrement sides


Mobile Controls
[Double Tap] Toggle Dark Mode
[Swipe Up] Increment speed
[Swipe Down] Decrement speed
[Swipe Left] Decrement sides
[Swipe Right] Increment sides
